  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This pilot study compares the effect of working memory training and neurofeedback in
      non-medicated children age 7 to 13 years with ADHD. Half of the participants will receive
      working memory training, while the other half will receive neurofeedback.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
